genresAdvancedInfo.name: maltese hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Emerging in the 1990s, Maltese hip hop is a unique blend of traditional Maltese music and modern hip hop beats. It often features lyrics that tackle social and political issues, as well as personal struggles and experiences. Maltese hip hop artists have gained popularity both locally and internationally.
